ollapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        </ul></div></div></div><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><div><div class=\"main-image\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/71071/GNEvhx9dGTsZxc4g4tjKnOPr9xycPA-metadW5kZWZpbmVkVW50aXRsZWQtMS5qcGc=-.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table><tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">NATURAL WOOD GRAIN: Please note that items may vary in color and grain due to the natural acacia wood material of these wooden kitchen utensils and kitchen utensil sets</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FOOD SAFE KITCHEN UTENSILS: Natural acacia wooden cooking utensils are safe for all food and meal prep, cooking and baking; the wooden kitchen utensils are safe to use with ceramic or non stick pots, pans and other cookware</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SOLID ACACIA WOOD COOKING UTENSILS: Acacia wood kitchen utensils features a comfortable rounded handle, soft edges, natural wood grain and food safe finish; in addition to their practicality and versatility, they also add a welcomed dose of organic visual texture in the kitchen</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">KITCHEN ESSENTIALS: Solid acacia wooden kitchen utensils are a must have home essentials item you’ll reach for time and time again for meal prep, cooking, baking and serving; these cooking utensils features a timeless design, complemented by a soft and natural finish</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 12 x 3 x 0.5 inches approximately, styles vary; Dishwasher Safe: No</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>Labrea Life + Home Solid Acacia Wooden Kitchen Utensils Home Essentials (Assorted Styles and Packs)</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">49.99</span></h2>\n                <p>In opposition to harsh metal or manufactured silicone kitchen utensils, opt for a more a natural option in your kitchen with Labrea Life + Homes’ Solid Acacia Wooden Kitchen Utensils Collection.\n\nThese wooden kitchen utensils are firstly and importantly, food safe for all meal prep, cooking, baking, tasting and serving; furthermore, the wooden kitchen utensils won’t scratch or mark your pots and pans like other kitchen utensils can, especially where ceramic and non stick cookware or bakeware are concerned.\n\nMeeting at the corner of function and form, these classic wooden kitchen utensils features a comfortable, rounded handle for ease of use when stirring or mixing, soft, smooth edges, balanced weight, vintage details and natural wood grain finish. Whether for cooking pasta, mixing up homemade chocolate chip cookie batter or serving a fresh salad, you’ll reach for these wooden kitchen utensils home essentials item time and time again for their versatility and practicality across the kitchen.\n\nFeaturing a classic and simple design, we love these wooden kitchen utensils not only for their timelessness and quality material construction, but for the welcomed dose of soft and organic visual texture. Functional, stylish and reliable, these solid acacia wooden kitchen utensils will be a great addition to top drawer tools or countertop utensil crock for all your cooking and baking needs. Choose from a wooden cooking spoon, corner spoon, skimmer, solid spatula and slotted spatula or spurtle.\n\nPLEASE NOTE: Utensils may vary in color and grain striations, due to the natural acacia wood material \n\nCARE INSTRUCTIONS: To maintain finish and avoid cracking, hand washing is recommended; remove excess water after hand washing and leave to air dry</p></div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"><table></table>\n        </div>\n",
